<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ludwig XI., Friedrich III., und Ludwig XII., Grafen von Oettingen</head><p>Der Rat versichert die Freundschaft nach Herausgabe der beschlagnahmten Wägen Nürnberger Bürger aus Donauwörth.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="189v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l12"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Ludwıg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> den <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l13">vnd <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Ludwıg dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Ötıng<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l14"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> als eẅr gnade / etlıchen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> etwıeuıl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l16">geſchırre 
<add><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l15">mıt <expan>kawffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab></add> dıe nehſt von werde <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auwſʒ</expan> <expan>gıeng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hett </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l17"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / haben vns dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbracht vnd ʒu <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l18">daʒ Jn eẅr gnade / <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Jr hab vnd geſchirr . <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> geſchıkt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l19">vnd vollgen hab laſſen / Alſo wellen wır für vns vnd dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dıe des ʒuſchıcken gehabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l21">haben . von der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürbaſm<ex>er</ex></expan> keins argen <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l22">on geuerde / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="189v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> den <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Ludwig, dem <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu <expan>Öting<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ewr gnade etlichen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> etwievil geschirre <add>mit
                                    <expan>kawffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan></add>, die nehst von
                        Werde <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auwsz</expan><expan>gieng<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hett
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, haben uns die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbracht und zu
                            <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> getan, daz in ewr gnade
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> ir hab und geschirr
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> geschikt und vollgen hab lassen; also
                        wellen wir für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>, die des
                        zu schicken gehabt haben, von der sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürbasm<ex>er</ex></expan> keins argen
                            <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> on geverde. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
